 5:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='291375' id='t-291375'>Please -- don't tell me I'm normal.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='294607' id='t-294607'>Thank you. (Applause)</span>
